SummaryTextDescription: Set on a generous plot with further potential to extend, subject to the usual consents, is this spacious five bedroom, four reception room detached family home. The property has a 14ft master bedroom with en-suite and views over London towards Canary Wharf. There is a further en-suite to the second bedroom, ground floor cloakroom, a wonderful 15ft orangery and a 17ft kitchen/breakfast room. The rear garden measures 63ft x 70ft and there is a double garage with parking also to the front. The Summit is a cul-de-sac located opposite Epping Forest and also within the Staples Road school catchment.
